<h1>Personality Disorders</h1>

<p>There are a lot of personality disorders. In this section, we will review only some of them. You will find a lot of links to the resources where you can find out more. </p>
    
<h2>Below you can find a list of personality Disorders</h2>

<ul style="list-style-type:disc;">
    
  <li>Antisocial personality disorder</li>
  <li>Avoidant personality disorder</li>
  <li>Borderline personality disorder</li>
  <li>Dependent personality disorder</li>
  <li>Histrionic personality disorder</li>
  <li>Narcissistic personality disorder</li>
  <li>Obsessive-compulsive personality disorder</li>
    <li>Paranoid personality disorder</li>
    <li>Schizoid personality disorder</li>
    <li>Schizotypal personality disorder</li>
</ul>  
    <p> If you want to find out more about any of the disorders listed above, you can visit American Psychiatric Association <a href="https://www.psychiatry.org/patients-families/personality-disorders/what-are-personality-disorders">website</a>. 
    </p>
    
<p>
   Personality disorders are usually diagnosed in individuals over 18 as this is when person forms his/her own personality. There are couple factors that can be a reason for developing this disease:
    </p>
    
    <ul style="list-style-type:square;">
    
  <li>Geans.You can inherit this disorder form older generation</li>
  <li>Enviroment can play a big role: how you were raised, where, what kind of parents did you have?</li>
  
</ul> 
    <p>
    All of that can play an important role in forming your personality. For more information visit MayoClinic <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/personality-disorders/symptoms-causes/syc-20354463">official website</a>
    </p>
    
    <h3>Treatment</h3>
    <p>
    There is no universal treatment for personality disorders. Here is some methods which can be helpful:
    </p>
    
    <ul style="list-style-type:circle;">
    
  <li>Therapy</li>
   <li>Psychiatric medications</li>
      <li>Psychiatric medications</li>
        <li>Outpatient/inpatient hospital problems</li>
  
</ul> 
    
    <p>
    If you also suffer from symptoms of depression and anxiety you can find some exercises and techniques on our website. For more information about personality disorders treatment visit <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/personality-disorders/diagnosis-treatment/drc-20354468">MayoClinic website</a>
    
    </p>
    <p><center>Thank you your visit, hope you have a wonderful day!!!! </center>
    
